description: This cluster, to be used in conjunction with the OSRS CMCF Block-H mapping, covers BLS NAICS class codes ranging from 301 to 600.
name: BLS-301-THRU-600

values.description: Industries in the Food Manufacturing subsector transform livestock and agricultural products into products for intermediate or final consumption. The industry groups are distinguished by the raw materials (generally of animal or vegetable origin) processed into food products.
